</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div id="siteTitle"> Ruby on Rails 4 biblioteka: Rusmir Gadžo </div>
    <div id="sitePhoto">
      <div id="sitePhotoDesc">Ruby on Rails tutorial</div>
